{"id":693,"date":"2024-08-02T20:13:10","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T20:13:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=693"},"modified":"2024-08-02T20:13:10","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T20:13:10","slug":"tm044-rest","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm044-rest\/","title":{"rendered":"TM044 Rest"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM044 Rest<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Found in the Crater Town Valley Cave B1F directly North of the ladder leading out of the cave. Requires Surf.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>The user sleeps for two turns to fully restore HP and any status problems.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Psychic<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Valley Cave<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/\">Surf<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Starting from outside of the Crater Town Pok\u00e9mon Center, you want to go North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-crater-town-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Crater Town Pok\u00e9mon Center \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Crater Town Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go to the center of Crater Town\u2019s crater and enter Valley Cave. <\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-valley-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Entering Valley Cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering Valley Cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once inside, head West and take the ladder to go deeper into the cave.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-ladder-to-go-deeper-inside-of-the-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the ladder to go deeper inside of the cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the ladder to go deeper inside of the cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From here, you want to follow the cave South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-following-the-cave-south.jpg\" alt=\"Following the cave South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the cave South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll shortly have to cross two blue and white bridges, indicating you\u2019re on the right path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-crossing-2-bridges-to-continue-going-south.jpg\" alt=\"Crossing two bridges to continue going South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Crossing two bridges to continue going South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually come across a ladder at the very end of the cave leading you outside. <\/p>\n<p>Instead of taking that, hug the West wall and follow the narrow path North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-following-the-narrow-path-north.jpg\" alt=\"Following the narrow path North. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the narrow path North.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The TM for Rest is found at the end of this path and is reachable by using Surf.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/07-pokemon-unbound-finding-rest-at-the-end-of-the-hidden-path.jpg\" alt=\"Finding Rest at the end of the hidden path. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding Rest at the end of the hidden path.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":694,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[8],"class_list":["post-693","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tms-hms"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/693","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/139"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/694"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=693"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=693"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}